    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快离开地面！！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《离开蠕虫镇的最后一班火车》是一款混乱的非对称沙虫对牛仔在线多人游戏，其中蠕虫只能看到接触地面的玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/f2e2ace5f33a362ef943f088ae00edc4.poster.avif?t=1752864862\" width=608 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/f2e2ace5f33a362ef943f088ae00edc4.webm?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/f2e2ace5f33a362ef943f088ae00edc4.mp4?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扮演牛仔</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他牛仔合作完成目标，逃出蠕虫镇！但要小心，触碰沙地会暴露你的位置，引来沙虫。如果你想活下来，你需要奔跑、跳跃、攀爬，并利用强大的工具逃脱这个险恶的环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/e2dec396dcc850eed078d26e38c710c6.poster.avif?t=1752864862\" width=608 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/e2dec396dcc850eed078d26e38c710c6.webm?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/e2dec396dcc850eed078d26e38c710c6.mp4?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><br><strong>扮演沙虫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感觉饿了吗？扮演沙虫，阻止那些讨厌的牛仔离开小镇。凭借一系列特殊技能和极高速度的地下潜行能力，他们很快就会成为沙虫的食物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/8d06c528624eca8339c32f4717d94379.poster.avif?t=1752864862\" width=608 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/8d06c528624eca8339c32f4717d94379.webm?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/8d06c528624eca8339c32f4717d94379.mp4?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><strong>朋友通行证！只有房主需要购买游戏</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用创新的朋友通行证系统，只有大厅的房主需要购买游戏。其他所有玩家都可以完全免费加入大厅！这使《沙虫镇》成为朋友聚会、游戏之夜以及主播与社区一起玩的完美选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/5ebdfec8ebc38bbfde232fddcb4340bf.avif?t=1752864862\" width=608 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义、挑战以及更多内容！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入的玩家自定义，适用于牛仔和沙虫</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16人大厅</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公共大厅浏览器**</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100多个挑战可完成，并解锁可自定义的外观**</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机地图布局让每一局《沙虫镇》都独一无二</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有趣且充满节庆氛围的地图主题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全可自定义的比赛设置，能够精准适配您的玩家群体 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**这些功能在朋友通行证中不可用</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/df26ad64efd4200d720a3d18c3d1be9e.poster.avif?t=1752864862\" width=608 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/df26ad64efd4200d720a3d18c3d1be9e.webm?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318480/extras/df26ad64efd4200d720a3d18c3d1be9e.mp4?t=1752864862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
